title: Lunar Love Spacedrop #1
body:
Lunar Love Spacedrop is an initiative to invite more explorers to join the community with a surprise MOONS airdrop.

1. MoonTools has created a wallet where 1500 MOONS from the marketing funds have been allocated

2. Every full moon (~once a month), we will airdrop 10% of these MOONS to holders of a token that is voted by the community of MOONS holders

3. This wallet is open to contribution of MOONS if you wish to give this initiative a boost

Spacedrop Wallet Address: 0x8c9E77B356622d46D3b853e79e14dDE05f2dF6a7

---

Mission 1: 
150 holders of the voted token will receive an airdrop of 1 MOONS (before public contribution). Wallets already holding MOONS will be excluded.

Airdrop will take place after voting ends. Subsequent airdrops will take place on full moons. Please cast your vote below!
author: 0x9be82c0E5B75C53F32E63b40442E9dA8cCA06f21
